Class ANNFilterItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amdocs.oss.ann.integration.rest.model.ANNFilterItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ANNFilterItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Author:
    MVEKSLER Request Filter Item is a part of the request filters list and defines the objects selection logic tag - defines if the field represents Value or ID. ENUM{VALUE, ID} name - filter field name values - the list of the filter values caseSensitive - [true/false] operator - ENUM{EQUAL, NOT_EQUAL, STARTS_WITH, CONTAINS,LIKE, NOT_NULL,IS_NULL,LESS_THAN, GREATER_THAN, IN, BETWEEN} listOperator - ENUM{OR}
    See Also:
